import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    data['origin_destination'] = data['origin'] + '-' + data['destination']
    data_sorted = data.sort_values('count', ascending=False)
    
    ax = data_sorted.plot.bar(x='origin_destination', y='count', legend=False)
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.set_xlabel('Origin-Destination Combination')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('What is the most popular origin and destination combination?', wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data.groupby('origin')['count'].sum().plot(kind='bar')
    plt.xlabel('Origin')
    plt.ylabel('Count')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of counts for each origin?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
        plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    avg_count = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).mean().reset_index()
    pivot_table = avg_count.pivot('origin', 'destination', 'count')
    
    ax = plt.axes()
    heatmap = ax.imshow(pivot_table, cmap='coolwarm', interpolation='nearest')
    plt.colorbar(heatmap)
    
    ax.set_xticks(range(len(pivot_table.columns)))
    ax.set_yticks(range(len(pivot_table.index)))
    ax.set_xticklabels(pivot_table.columns)
    ax.set_yticklabels(pivot_table.index)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.xlabel('Destination')
    plt.ylabel('Origin')
    plt.title('What is the average count for each origin-destination combination?', wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
